I moved Secret Book of FRC LabVIEW from my google drive to Github.

I also added copies of control theory training presentations done a few years ago. The training is not specific to LabVIEW, however all the samples use LabVIEW. It also doesn’t exactly follow the what is in the “secret book” but there are similarities…

Secret book of FRC LabVIEW version 2.x. Contribute to jsimpso81/FRC_Secret_Book_Of_FRC_LabVIEW_2 development by creating an account on GitHub.
